import React from "react"
import {
    BrowserRouter as Router,
    Routes,
    Route,
    Link
} from "react-router-dom"
import Home from "./pages/Home"

function App(){
    return
    <Router>
        <Routes>
            <Route path="/perfil">
                <Home/>
            </Route>
        </Routes>
    </Router>
    
}

export default App
